13... Rd8 14. e5 Ne8 15. exd6 Bxd6 16. Ne4 {White has a winning attack. Black
resigned in a few moves.} Bf8 17. Neg5 f5 18. Qe2 h6 19. Nxe6 Nb4 20. Nxd8
Nxa2+ 21. Kb1 Nb4 22. Qxe8 {1-0 Black resigns.} 1-0

