1. e4 c5 2. Nc3 Nc6 3. Bb5 e6 4. Bxc6 bxc6 5. d3 d6 6. f4 Qh4+ $2 {The check
does not achieve anything- White does not mind playing g3. Black does not have
access to the light squares on the kingside} 7. g3 Qd8 8. Nf3 h5 9. h3 Be7 10.
Qe2 Rb8 11. b3 $1 {stabilizing the queenside} Nf6 12. Na4 $6 (12. Bd2 $1 Qc7
13. Na4 d5 14. c4 $18) 12... c4 $1 13. dxc4 (13. bxc4 Qa5+) 13... d5 14. Ng5
Ba6 15. Be3 Bxc4 16. Qd2 $1 Bb5 17. Nc5 Nd7 18. Ncxe6 fxe6 19. Nxe6 Qc8 20.
Nxg7+ Kf7 21. Nf5 Nf6 22. Nxe7 Kxe7 23. exd5 cxd5 24. O-O-O Qf5 25. Bd4 Ne4 26.
Qb4+ Nd6 27. Rhe1+ Kd7 28. Bxh8 Rxh8 29. Re5 Qf6 30. Rexd5 Qa1+ 31. Kd2 1-0

