will eventually consolidate and win the c5 pawn} Rd3 15. Re1 Rhd8 16. Kb1 g5
17. Kc2 gxf4 18. Bxf4) 14... Kc7 15. Rad1 Bc8 16. h3 a5 17. Rxd8 Rxd8 18. Ne1
