{How should White continue?} 1. c4 Nc7 (1... Ndb4 2. a3) (1... Qa5+ 2. Kf1 $1 (
2. Qd2 $5 Ndb4 3. Kf1 Nd4 $1 4. Nc3 $14) 2... Nc7 3. Bxc6 $3 $16) 2. Bxc6 $3
